{"parse":{"title":"Exclusive Equipment","pageid":6000,"revid":38260,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\">\n</p><aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-wikia pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">Exclusive Equipment</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"type\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Type</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Game_Systems\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Game Systems\">Game Systems</a></div>\n</div>\n</aside>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p><b>Exclusive Equipments</b> are unique items assigned to each Hero, providing exclusive effects tailored to their abilities.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Overview\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Overview</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Unlocking\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Unlocking</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Upgrading\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Upgrading</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Change_History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Change History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Overview\">Overview</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FExclusive_Equipment%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Every Hero in the game possesses a distinct Exclusive Equipment with unique effects designed specifically for them. The Exclusive Equipment is unlocked separately for each Hero when they reach the Mythic+ rarity, starting at level 0. Unlocking this weapon grants the Hero a new skill, sometimes significantly enhancing their power.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Unlocking\">Unlocking</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FExclusive_Equipment%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When a Hero reaches Mythic+, their Exclusive Equipment becomes available for unlocking and enhancement. This weapon grants unique stats customized for that Hero and unlocks a fourth ability in their kit, referred to as an Exclusive Skill (EX).\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Upgrading\">Upgrading</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fafk-journey.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FExclusive_Equipment%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D3&amp;uselang=en&amp;metadata=article-registration-edit-article-section\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\" aria-label=\"Sign in to edit\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Exclusive Equipments can be upgraded in the Hero Upgrade screen. Every +5 level unlocks a new ability or enhances an existing one.\n</p>\n<ul><li>The upgrade path follows a structured progression, with each level requiring specific resources.</li>\n<li>The table below details the upgrade path, including costs and abilities unlocked at each stage.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Level\n</th>\n<th>Upgrade Tier\n</th>\n<th>Unlocks\n</th>\n<th>Hero Tier Required\n</th>\n<th>Cost\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0 to +5</td>\n<td>Stats, Ability Upgrade</td>\n<td>Mythic+</td>\n<td><span class=\"item\"><span class=\"item-image\"><span class=\"hidden\" data-size=\"30\" style=\"height:30px;width:30px\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Tidal_Essence\" title=\"Tidal Essence\"><img alt=\"Tidal Essence\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/1/17/Item_Tidal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210829\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Item Tidal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Tidal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></span><span class=\"mobile-only\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Tidal_Essence\" title=\"Tidal Essence\"><img alt=\"Tidal Essence\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/1/17/Item_Tidal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210829\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Item Tidal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Tidal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"item-text\"> <a href=\"/wiki/Tidal_Essence\" title=\"Tidal Essence\">Tidal Essence</a> \u00d7150</span></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>+6 to +10</td>\n<td>Stats, Ability Upgrade</td>\n<td>Supreme</td>\n<td><span class=\"item\"><span class=\"item-image\"><span class=\"hidden\" data-size=\"30\" style=\"height:30px;width:30px\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\"><img alt=\"Temporal Essence\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/4/42/Item_Temporal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210837\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"Item Temporal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Temporal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></span><span class=\"mobile-only\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\"><img alt=\"Temporal Essence\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Item Temporal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Temporal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/4/42/Item_Temporal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210837\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"item-text\"> <a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\">Temporal Essence</a> \u00d775</span></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>+11 to +15</td>\n<td>Stats, Ability Upgrade</td>\n<td>Supreme+</td>\n<td><span class=\"item\"><span class=\"item-image\"><span class=\"hidden\" data-size=\"30\" style=\"height:30px;width:30px\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\"><img alt=\"Temporal Essence\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Item Temporal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Temporal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/4/42/Item_Temporal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210837\" /></a></span></span><span class=\"mobile-only\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\"><img alt=\"Temporal Essence\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIABAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAEALAAAAAABAAEAQAICTAEAOw%3D%3D\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"23\" height=\"30\" class=\"mw-file-element lazyload\" data-image-name=\"Item Temporal Essence.png\" data-image-key=\"Item_Temporal_Essence.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" data-src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/afk-journey/images/4/42/Item_Temporal_Essence.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/23?cb=20240319210837\" /></a></span></span></span><span class=\"item-text\"> <a href=\"/wiki/Temporal_Essence\" title=\"Temporal Essence\">Temporal Essence</a> \u00d7200</span></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>+16 to +20</td>\n<td>Stats</td>\n<td>Supreme+</td>\n<td><span class=\"item\"><span class=\"item-image\"><span class=\"hidden\" data-size=\"30\" style=\"height:30px;width:30px\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Twilight_Essence\" title=\"Twilight Essenc